774
00:54:30,976 --> 00:54:32,018
[shocked groan]

775
00:54:34,604 --> 00:54:35,855
[groans]

776
00:54:43,530 --> 00:54:44,447
[gasps]

777
00:54:45,448 --> 00:54:46,449
[groans]

778
00:54:49,035 --> 00:54:50,203
[groans]

779
00:54:54,332 --> 00:54:55,333
[yells]

780
00:54:56,126 --> 00:54:58,503
[wails]

781
00:55:01,006 --> 00:55:04,092
[sobs softly]

782
00:55:12,309 --> 00:55:15,437
[newscaster] <i>Many mysteries unsolved</i>
<i>in the case of the Human Vapor.</i>

783
00:55:15,520 --> 00:55:16,604
ONE YEAR LATER

784
00:55:16,688 --> 00:55:19,232
<i>New information has emerged</i>
<i>regarding a connection between him</i>

785
00:55:19,316 --> 00:55:20,984
<i>and former reporter Kyoko Kono.</i>

786
00:55:21,943 --> 00:55:24,696
<i>Witnesses have revealed</i>
<i>that the two individuals in question</i>

787
00:55:24,779 --> 00:55:27,741
<i>were forced into illegal labor</i>
<i>at White Center,</i>

788
00:55:27,824 --> 00:55:29,993
<i>and they both lived there</i>
<i>during the same period.</i>

789
00:55:30,076 --> 00:55:33,955
<i>This suggests they knew each other</i>
<i>before the Human Vapor attacks began.</i>

790
00:55:34,456 --> 00:55:37,208
<i>To this day,</i>
<i>their whereabouts remain unknown.</i>

791
00:55:37,792 --> 00:55:39,419
<i>According to sources, one year ago,</i>

792
00:55:39,502 --> 00:55:42,797
<i>an officer and from the Metropolitan</i>
<i>Police Department witnessed the moment</i>

793
00:55:42,881 --> 00:55:45,800
<i>Kono the Human Vapor seemingly vanished.</i>

794
00:55:45,884 --> 00:55:48,261
<i>This strange occurrence took place</i>
<i>inside a vault</i>

795
00:55:48,345 --> 00:55:50,930
<i>in the basement of the old JNT building.</i>

796
00:55:51,014 --> 00:55:53,850
<i>Police believe the two</i>
<i>may have disappeared intentionally</i>

797
00:55:53,933 --> 00:55:55,852
<i>in order to avoid arrest.</i>

798
00:55:55,935 --> 00:55:58,271
[wistful piano music playing]

799
00:55:58,355 --> 00:56:00,565
This is, uh… Who are you?

800
00:56:01,066 --> 00:56:04,444
Tatsuya Nishiyama. I'm from JNT.

801
00:56:04,944 --> 00:56:06,529
[Michiko] Right. Yes.

802
00:56:07,572 --> 00:56:09,824
So, how can I help you?

803
00:56:10,325 --> 00:56:14,621
It's a request from the PR office,
looking to do a piece on what we do here.

804
00:56:14,704 --> 00:56:16,998
It's for Police 24 Hours or something.

805
00:56:18,041 --> 00:56:19,667
You're doing a stakeout, right?

806
00:56:20,168 --> 00:56:22,587
Go along with her.
Feel free to ask whatever you want.

807
00:56:22,670 --> 00:56:24,547
[Michiko] Uh, hold on, Chief?

808
00:56:27,717 --> 00:56:29,052
Good to see you again.

809
00:56:30,470 --> 00:56:31,346
What?

810
00:56:32,180 --> 00:56:33,723
Have we met before?

811
00:56:33,807 --> 00:56:36,434
[Tatsuya] Yeah, a long time ago.

812
00:56:36,518 --> 00:56:38,603
We were working on the Human Vapor.

813
00:56:39,437 --> 00:56:41,356
Huh? Wait.

814
00:56:41,439 --> 00:56:43,817
In the parking lot? In Shizuoka?

815
00:56:43,900 --> 00:56:45,860
That's the one. You got it.

816
00:56:47,112 --> 00:56:48,738
[both chuckle]

817
00:56:49,406 --> 00:56:52,033
- Okay. Shall we head out?
- Sure.

818
00:56:53,243 --> 00:56:54,244
[Tatsuya] Wow.

819
00:56:56,246 --> 00:56:57,664
[Michiko] Seriously.

820
00:57:00,125 --> 00:57:02,043
Last year was a lot, wasn't it?

821
00:57:04,462 --> 00:57:05,880
It sure was, yeah.

822
00:57:06,506 --> 00:57:08,007
Could've done with less.

823
00:57:11,136 --> 00:57:15,181
[Kaho] Welcome to horror paradise!
Let's go.

824
00:57:15,682 --> 00:57:19,686
How are all you killers doing tonight?
Bloody awesome?

825
00:57:20,186 --> 00:57:23,690
[sighs] I can't even believe
what I'm seeing.

826
00:57:23,773 --> 00:57:25,650
We are now at ten

827
00:57:26,401 --> 00:57:28,194
<i>million subscribers!</i>

828
00:57:29,779 --> 00:57:31,281
<i>Yay!</i>

829
00:57:31,364 --> 00:57:34,159
<i>Hey, Fujita, did you hear the news?</i>

830
00:57:34,659 --> 00:57:35,702
<i>We did it.</i>

831
00:57:36,202 --> 00:57:38,079
<i>We got here in one year.</i>

832
00:57:39,038 --> 00:57:42,459
<i>It's wild, hmm? But you know what?</i>

833
00:57:43,918 --> 00:57:45,170
<i>We're not finished yet!</i>

834
00:57:45,253 --> 00:57:48,089
<i>Killers, you need to know something</i>
<i>about my brother, okay?</i>

835
00:57:48,173 --> 00:57:50,967
<i>Fujita wanted to become</i>
<i>the world's number one streamer.</i>

836
00:57:51,050 --> 00:57:52,218
<i>That was his dream.</i>

837
00:57:52,719 --> 00:57:55,805
<i>I'm sorry to say he's threatened</i>
<i>to haunt us if you don't subscribe.</i>

838
00:57:55,889 --> 00:57:59,392
<i>So make sure you follow to join</i>
<i>Fujita and Kaho's Terror Zone,</i>

839
00:57:59,476 --> 00:58:01,561
<i>and don't forget to ring that bell</i>
<i>while you're at it!</i>

840
00:58:01,644 --> 00:58:04,063
Because if you don't support us,

841
00:58:04,147 --> 00:58:08,485
then the spirit of the man himself
will haunt you!

842
00:58:10,945 --> 00:58:12,322
[gasps twice]

843
00:58:12,906 --> 00:58:15,992
Illuminati! How did you find us? [gasps]

844
00:58:16,075 --> 00:58:18,328
I'm so sorry, killers,
but that's it for today.

845
00:58:18,411 --> 00:58:19,496
[screams]

846
00:58:19,579 --> 00:58:22,332
"I'm here, my sister!"

847
00:58:22,415 --> 00:58:23,917
[choking]

848
00:58:24,000 --> 00:58:27,712
No! Stop!
Get out of my head! No, no! Stop!

849
00:58:27,795 --> 00:58:30,340
"Kaho, I still have so much to say!
Don't go!"

850
00:58:30,423 --> 00:58:32,800
Get out of my head! Stop! No!

851
00:58:35,637 --> 00:58:37,639
[music fades out]

